## Usage

### GitHub Actions

```yaml
name: MegaLinter
on: [push, pull_request]

jobs:
  lint:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - name: Checkout Code
        uses: actions/checkout@v4
        with:
          token: ${{ "{{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}" }}
          fetch-depth: 0

      - name: MegaLinter
        uses: docker://{{ registry }}/{{ repository }}/megalinter-custom-flavor:latest
        env:
          GITHUB_TOKEN: ${{ "{{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}" }}
```

### Docker

```bash
docker run --rm \
  -v ${PWD}:/tmp/lint \
  {{ registry }}/{{ repository }}/megalinter-custom-flavor:latest
```

